                        <label><input type="radio" name="compare" value="3" required> 3 </label>
                        <label><input type="radio" name="compare" value="4" required> 4 </label>
                        <label><input type="radio" name="compare" value="5" required> 5 </label>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td>
                        <label for="feel">Following the previous question, how do you feel about these comparisons, generally speaking?</label>
                      </td>
                      <td>
                        <label><input type="radio" name="feel" value="1" required> 1 </label>
                        <label><input type="radio" name="feel" value="2" required> 2 </label>
                        <label><input type="radio" name="feel" value="3" required> 3 </label>
                        <label><input type="radio" name="feel" value="4" required> 4 </label>
                        <label><input type="radio" name="feel" value="5" required> 5 </label>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td>
                        <label for="validation">How often do you look to seek validation from features on social media?</label>
                      </td>
                      <td>
                        <label><input type="radio" name="validation" value="1" required> 1 </label>
                        <label><input type="radio" name="validation" value="2" required> 2 </label>
                        <label><input type="radio" name="validation" value="3" required> 3 </label>
                        <label><input type="radio" name="validation" value="4" required> 4 </label>
                        <label><input type="radio" name="validation" value="5" required> 5 </label>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
